[PROMPT] Design a dynamic component 10 and also intersection observer fade-in [CODE] <!-- Composite Elite -->
<div style="padding: 20px; background: #3b82f6; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">Dynamic Pro Component 10</div>
<script>const obs = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => { entries.forEach(e => { if(e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add("visible"); }); }); document.querySelectorAll(".fade").forEach(el => obs.observe(el));</script> [END]

<script>const obs = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => { entries.forEach(e => { if(e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add("visible"); }); }); document.querySelectorAll(".fade").forEach(el => obs.observe(el));</script> [END]

[PROMPT] Design a dynamic component 38 and also intersection observer fade-in [CODE] <!-- Composite Elite -->
<div style="padding: 20px; background: #6366f1; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">Dynamic Pro Component 38</div>
<script>const obs = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => { entries.forEach(e => { if(e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add("visible"); }); }); document.querySelectorAll(".fade").forEach(el => obs.observe(el));</script> [END]
